        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Congress Commission Act</b></p> <p>This bill establishes the Congressional Commission to Strengthen Representative Democracy, which must examine and make recommendations relating to changing the membership size of the House of Representatives and the method of electing Representatives.</p>]]></text>
